title: Alien Skin Software Photo Bundle Collection (05.2018) Full With
description:
Alien Skin Software Photo Bundle Collection (05.2018)

Photo Bundle collection a collection of plug-ins and graphic filters for Adobe Photoshop, Elements and Lightroom, which will be useful both for beginners and professional designers. With them you can easily and accurately process or decorate your images, change photos by adding various effects.

The structure includes:
Alien Skin Blow Up 3.1.0.157
Alien Skin Exposure X3 3.5.1.137
Alien Skin Exposure X3 Bundle 3.5.4.114
Alien Skin Eye Candy 7 7.2.0.50
Alien Skin Snap Art 4.1.0.151

Description of the programs:
The Exposure X Bundle is a photo editor and organizer that combines all the plug-ins from Alien Skin’s for editing photos in one product. The basis of the kit is Exposure X, photo editing application that optimizes the workflow and provides a wide range of creative tools. Also in this kit are two additional applications for expanding creative possibilities: Blow Up 3, which is designed to increase the size of images with maximum preservation of their quality and Snap Art 4, which turns your photos into magnificent handmade paintings.

Main features:
All filter groups are united into a single interface.
Filters: Colored pencils, Comics, Impasto, Oil paint, Pastel, Pencil drawing, Drawing with pen and ink, Pointillism, Stylization, Watercolor, Drawing with colored chalk.
Close integration with Lightroom and support for batch processing (Photoshop is not required)
